name: Manifold Finance
introduce: Manifold Finance enables and provides access to high-value transaction pools on EVM-compatible chains, through infrastructure: SecureRPC. Manifold Finance aggregates multiple endpoints along with maintaining direct access to disparate mining pools/validator nodes. Manifold Finance’s first solution, OpenMEV (formerly known as YCabal) is an aggregation strategy for scaling layer one using a mix of MEV and smart contract techniques to scale services like SushiSwap for end users.
